'''2021年世界速度滑冰锦标赛'''于2021年2月11日至14日在荷兰海伦芬进行<ref name="isuannouncement">{{cite web|url=https://www.schaatsen.nl/media/47403/wssc-announcement.pdf|title=ISU World Speed Skating Championships Heerenveen 2021|work=KNSB|accessdate=2021-03-02|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210302071223/https://www.schaatsen.nl/media/47403/wssc-announcement.pdf|archivedate=2021-03-02}}</ref>。此次比赛原定于2021年2月25日至28日在[[中国|中国]][[北京|北京]][[国家速滑馆|国家速滑馆]]进行，作为[[2022年冬季奥林匹克运动会|2022年北京冬奥]][[2022年冬季奥林匹克运动会速度滑冰比赛|速度滑冰项目]]的测试赛<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chinanews.com/ty/2020/04-13/9155491.shtml|title=北京冬奥速滑测试赛敲定 明年2月“冰丝带”开战|publisher=中国新闻网|date=2020-04-13|accessdate=2021-03-02|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200420175444/http://www.chinanews.com/ty/2020/04-13/9155491.shtml|archivedate=2020-04-20}}</ref>。然而受[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2019冠状病毒病疫情]]影响，中国放弃了该赛事主办权，该赛事也不再是冬奥测试赛<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1100844/isu-seeking-new-venues-for-test-events|title=ISU seek new venue for World Speed Skating Championships after Beijing 2022 test events cancelled|work=Inside the Games|date=2020-11-16|accessdate=2021-03-02|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116172947/https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1100844/isu-seeking-new-venues-for-test-events|archivedate=2020-11-16}}</ref>。最终荷兰海伦芬获得该赛事的主办权，比赛也被重新安排到2021年2月11日至14日进行<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.isu.org/speed-skating/events/heerenveen-hub-2021|title=
ISU Speed Skating Hub 2021|work=[[国际滑冰联盟|International Skating Union]]|accessdate=2021-03-02|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110114202/https://www.isu.org/speed-skating/events/heerenveen-hub-2021|archivedate=2021-01-10}}</ref>。

比赛开赛时，全球依旧受[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2019冠状病毒病疫情]]困扰，为防止感染扩大，国际滑冰联盟针对包括该赛事在内的所有2020–21赛季的国际速度滑冰比赛出台了相应措施，包括限制相关人员与外界的接触、强制相关人员在规定场合下佩戴[[口罩|口罩]]、定期对相关人员进行[[2019冠状病毒病检测|病毒检测]]等<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.isu.org/docman-documents-links/isu-files/documents-communications/clean-sport-1/coronavirus/25276-speed-skating-bubble-heerenveen-health-regulations-for-participating-teams/file|title=2020-2021 ISU Events Speed Skating (Heerenveen) COVID-19 Measures|work=International Skating Union|date=2020-12-01|accessdate=2021-03-02|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129223323/https://www.isu.org/docman-documents-links/isu-files/documents-communications/clean-sport-1/coronavirus/25276-speed-skating-bubble-heerenveen-health-regulations-for-participating-teams/file|archivedate=2021-01-29}}</ref>。

由于[[国际体育仲裁法庭|国际体育仲裁法庭]]于2020年12月17日作出判决，禁止存在[[俄羅斯體育禁藥|国家级体育禁药问题]]的[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]]在两年内以国家名义参加国际大赛<ref>{{cite web|url=https://apnews.com/article/russia-banned-name-flag-olympic-games-a8bd342806883f66152859701d5ae5d4|title=Russia can't use its name and flag at the next 2 Olympics|first=Graham|last=Dunbar|date=2020-12-17|access-date=2020-12-17|publisher=[[美联社|Associated Press]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217152124/https://apnews.com/article/russia-banned-name-flag-olympic-games-a8bd342806883f66152859701d5ae5d4|archivedate=2020-12-17}}</ref>，该队在该赛事以“俄罗斯滑冰联盟”（{{lang|en|Russian Skating Union}}，缩写：{{lang|en|RSU}}）的名义参加比赛<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1104229/golikova-dubreuil-speed-skating-worlds|title=Dubreuil and Golikova win 500m titles at ISU World Speed Skating Championships|work=Inside the Games|date=2021-02-12|accessdate=2021-03-02|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210212192937/https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1104229/golikova-dubreuil-speed-skating-worlds|archivedate=2021-02-12}}</ref>。

